\p 
\v 1 Zozuwe zaai ma, Izilay…õle nuiti ti ∆ď…Ēo…†…Ē GALAGI …†aaza…†ani, ti …†…õ ma: ¬ęGi zaama, …ď…õ …†a a li m…Ēunpa, eŐĀ k…Ē…Ēi  č…õ…õ Kanaan nuiti ba?¬Ľ
